result.title: Submitting problem to COCI
result.content: I've searched and searched for a proper place to submit COCI problems and there just aren't any that are constantly updated and contain the entire archive. The best I've found for now is DMOJ, but it's still not updated to a satisfactory level. Is there any online judge I might have missed? Is there a group on CF that contains the problems? And can the admins add the problems to Gym?
